      "description": "This vehicle is in good, reliable condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The exterior finish is clean and glossy, though a close inspection will reveal some minor stone chips on the hood and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is well-preserved with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster and common touchpoints. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a documented service history, making it an excellent choice for someone looking for a dependable car that still shows very well.",
