      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This exceptional vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector. Maintained to an uncompromising standard, it remains in showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear. Its mechanical integrity and aesthetic preservation are absolute, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from its original delivery. We invite serious inquiries for this peerless acquisition.",
